9:- Which property controls the image scroll in the background ?
Ans:- background image scroll property use to the background-attachment property

Example of scroll background

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <title>Background Scroll</title>
    <style>
        body {
            background-image: url("https://images.pexels.com/photos/1687944/pexels-photo-1687944.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=600");
            background-repeat: repeat-y;
            /* background-attachment: fixed; */
            background-attachment: scroll;
        }
    </style>
</head>

